Name: assign_worker_to_task
Description: Whether a worker is assigned to a specific task

Name: select_user_story_for_sprint
Description: Whether a user story is selected for the sprint backlog

Name: set_sprint_duration
Description: Duration of the sprint in days

Name: allocate_budget_to_feature
Description: Amount of budget allocated to a feature

Name: assign_role_to_worker
Description: Whether a role is assigned to a worker

Name: set_team_size
Description: Number of members in a team

Name: assign_skill_to_worker
Description: Whether a skill is assigned to a worker

Name: select_feature_for_release
Description: Whether a feature is included in a release plan

Name: set_task_effort
Description: Effort required for a task in hours

Name: set_stakeholder_relevance
Description: Relevance level of a stakeholder to a feature

Name: set_velocity_avg
Description: Average story points completed per sprint
